      "stem_html": "<p>The following reaction involves an intramolecular aldol reaction followed by a <i>retro</i> aldol-like reaction. Write both steps, and show their mechanisms.</p>\n<img class=\"scaled-down\" src=\"https://exercises.openstax.org/rails/active_storage/blobs/proxy/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBc1VZIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--1eaaef4fae17ee64a1a486572490f1c4a0af4565/OChem_23_EC_030.jpg\" alt=\"The intramolecular aldol reaction shows ethyl-2-oxo-1-(4-oxopentyl)cyclopentanecarboxylate with sodium ethoxide in ethanol, forming a cyclic nine-carbon chain compound with attached substituents.\">\n",
